"title": "8318: patience",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8318: patience",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of forbearance and self-control which shows itself particularly in a willingness to wait upon God and his will. Believers are called upon to be patient in their expectations of God's actions, and in their relationships with one another.</p>\n<h2>God's patience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:9\">ISA 48:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2\">ISA 65:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:13\">JOL 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">NAM 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25\">ROM 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:22\">ROM 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:20\">1PE 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>The patience of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17\">MAT 17:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:19\">MRK 9:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:41\">LUK 9:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:15\">2PE 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:21\">REV 2:21</a></p>\n<h2>Other examples of patience</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2TH 1:4</a> <em>the Thessalonian believers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:15\">HEB 6:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a> <em>Job</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:2\">REV 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Patience is part of the fruit of the Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10-Col1:11\">COL 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's people should exercise patience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:11\">PRO 19:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:29\">PRO 14:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:32\">PRO 16:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:15\">PRO 25:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:14-Matt6:15\">MAT 6:14–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:35\">MAT 18:35</a></p>\n<h2>People who need particular patience</h2>\n<h3>Christian leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10\">2TI 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Christian masters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Patience is necessary in church life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">1TH 5:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's word is to be received with patience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:22\">HEB 13:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:5\">PRO 2:1–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:3\">2TI 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Patience is a characteristic of love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:4\">1CO 13:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Patience is an aspect of faith and hope</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:20\">PSA 33:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:8\">JAS 5:7–5:8</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:2\">PSA 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:14\">PSA 27:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:7\">PSA 37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:34\">PSA 37:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:15\">PSA 38:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:166\">PSA 119:166</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:5-Ps130:6\">PSA 130:5–130:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:22\">PRO 20:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:17\">ISA 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:18\">ISA 30:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:24\">LAM 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:26\">LAM 3:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:4\">ACT 1:4</a> <em>Jesus Christ's instructions to the apostles to wait for the Holy Spirit</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:25\">ROM 8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13\">TIT 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">HEB 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:15\">HEB 6:15</a> <em>the example of Abraham</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:10\">JAS 5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:11\">REV 6:11</a></p>",
